45
00:03:29,036 --> 00:03:30,836
"Begitu"?

46
00:03:30,836 --> 00:03:36,536
Suatu saat, saingan tangguh bisa tiba-tiba muncul.

47
00:03:37,736 --> 00:03:40,936
Cabul! Orang ini cabul!

48
00:03:40,936 --> 00:03:42,436
Tidak, aku tidak...

49
00:03:42,436 --> 00:03:44,436
Jangan bertingkah lugu!

50
00:03:44,436 --> 00:03:46,636
Kau menyentuh bokongku sekarang!

51
00:03:46,636 --> 00:03:48,636
Ran, saatnya pembalasan!

52
00:03:49,536 --> 00:03:50,736
Tunggu.

53
